00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:05,000  
Dolphins are not fish, but rather warm-blooded mammals.

2  
00:00:05,100 --> 00:00:09,000  
They live in groups and communicate with each other using their own language.

3  
00:00:09,100 --> 00:00:13,000  
In this respect, they are similar to other animals, such as birds and bees.

4  
00:00:13,100 --> 00:00:17,000  
Dolphins are very different from land-dwelling mammals.

5  
00:00:17,100 --> 00:00:20,000  
Their brains are about the same size as ours.

6  
00:00:20,100 --> 00:00:24,000  
